#MaskSeries : GAJAH MINA

In Bali Mythology, Gajah Mina is a symbol of the power of the King of the Ocean, Dewa Baruna. Gajah Mina, also called Makara, has a connection with a story about saving the world by Avatara Vishnu or Matsya who has the form of a fish with the head of an elephant.
